'''Odiljon Hamrobekov''' (born 13 February 1996) is an Uzbek professional [[football (soccer)|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[Tractor S.C.|Tractor]] and the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]].<ref name="Soccerway">{{Soccerway|odiljon-khamrobekov/289109}}</ref>

==Career==
===Club===
On 23 July 2021, Hamrobekov returned to [[Pakhtakor Tashkent FK|Pakhtakor Tashkent]], signing a contract until the end of 2022.Currently playing for Bunyodkor FC, another team from the capital city.<ref>{{cite web |title=ОДИЛ ҲАМРОБЕКОВ "ПАХТАКОР"ГА ҚАЙТДИ |url=http://www.pakhtakor.uz/news/cnews/5651 |website=pakhtakor.uz/ |publisher=Pakhtakor Tashkent FK |access-date=23 July 2021 |language=Uzbek |date=23 July 2021}}</ref>

===International===
Hamrobekov made his international debut for [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan]] on 14 November 2017, during a friendly match against [[United Arab Emirates national football team|United Arab Emirates]].<ref>[https://www.national-football-teams.com/matches/report/18516/United_Arab_Emirates_Uzbekistan.html UAE 1–0 Uzbekistan]</ref>

